## Key Claims (fully reproducible)
- Crystalline vortex ejection velocity **≥ 1.85 Mm/s** in quartz/AlN lattice (193 THz pump)
- Sustained room-temperature polaritonic coherence (>50 µm)
- Energy & momentum conserved to ≤ 0.1 % over entire run
- No empirical fitting parameters — everything derived from conservation laws

## Quick Start – Reproduce the >1.8 Mm/s result in <10 minutes

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AmenRaAsar/drakarius-framework.git
cd drakarius-framework
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Flagship simulation
python simulations/vortex_propulsion.py --quick
